Transit Alarm helps you never miss your stop again! With over 7000 stops in the
Chicago area, we've got you covered. Simply select the stop you want to get off
at, and Transit Alarm will send you a notification when your stop is
approaching. Sleep, zone-out, and relax with confidence that you'll never miss
your stop again.

Transit Alarm has delightful graphics and an empathetic UI designed to delight
our users. More cities and real time updates coming soon!

